&lt;p>In the process of evolution humans acquired the capability of imagination. &lt;br>
This enables humans to think about the future. &lt;br>
That is why vision and visionary are most respected by sensible humans. &lt;br>
With this ability to think you can decide a goal, determine why that goal is important, and work on that goal.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>